[20.20 May 2: Circuit Breaker Day #26] Trying out Stir-fry Brinjal & Omni Meat with XO Sauce. 
Spotted @omnimeat by surprise at the supermarket (because SM FairPrice Finest was not listed in the list of outlets that sells). So happy to have spotted it, of course have to buy right!

Yummy! I hope I’m your neighbour 😂
@nettyliee Yes! Love to have this with porridge
Looks Yummy!!! But I don’t take brinjal!
Need to try the meat, but in another dish cos I don’t like brinjal 😬
Woah this is one of my fav dish!
I love brinjal with xo sauce too ☺️
Makes me really want to go try this Omni meat.
Omgggggggg! My daughter was asking me how does brinjal taste like? Can u cook for me to try? Cos daddy and mummy doesn eat brinjal. We nv cook before... 🤣🤣🤣
At first I thought it doesn’t taste nice. After trying out, it’s really Ok! My mom loves brinjal, so on and off she will cook this 😁 so I get to try !
@greenmonday_singapore My kids love it too! They said it tasted better than real meat! 😍😄
@xavvylicious Wow, really? That’s super good to hear! 🙌 Plant-based dishes can be delicious too~ 😋
Really glad that you like OmniMeat! 🙌😉
